asterisk-pjsip-cisco (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release — early 0.x; wants real-world testing before 1.0.
  * Ten shared modules: res_pjsip_cisco_{endpoint,
    pidf_body_generator, register_optionsind, bulkupdate,
    unsolicited_blf, service_control, feature_events, call_extras,
    remotecc, conference}.
  * Built and CI'd against Asterisk 20.x / 22.x / 23.x; bench-tested
    against a Cisco 7975 running Enterprise SIP firmware 9.4.2 on
    Asterisk 22.9.0.

